 "seller_info": {

        }
```
For the `item/itemAppInfo` endpoint, in the response you could find the id from the JSON path `productInfoComponent.adminSeq`:

 "productInfoComponent": {

```

Retrieves detailed seller info. **Note:** The `sellerId` parameter should not be confused with the Store Number displayed on the AliExpress website. Using an incorrect `sellerId` will result in a "not found" error message. Kindly check [this](https://ibb.co/pP4WVPh) image for more clarification:

For the `item/itemInfo` endpoint, in the response you could find the id from the JSON path `seller_info.nickname`:
```json
 "seller_info": {
        "nickname": "239194804", <---- use this
        "features": {
            "url": "https://www.aliexpress.com/store/1101351612", <--- don't use this
            "id": "246855432",
            "country": "China",
            "percentage": "93",
            "code": "EE",
            "count": "503222",
            "starts": "1022610600",
            "years": "3",
            "fans_num": "917861",
            "logo": "https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sd8de4bd7006644ea8821899a1f864918u.png"
        }
```
For the `item/itemAppInfo` endpoint, in the response you could find the id from the JSON path `productInfoComponent.adminSeq`:
```json
 "productInfoComponent": {
        "adminSeq": 239194804, <---- use this
        "categoryId": 70805,
        "categoryPaths": "7/200001081/200001082/70805",
        "fromTaobao": false,
        "id": 1005005120789585,
        "idStr": "1005005120789585",
        "lot": false,
        "maxPrice": 81.06,
        "minPrice": 77.5,
        "multiCurrencyDisplayPrice": "$77.50 - $81.06",
        "multiUnitName": "Pieces",
        "numberPerLot": 1,
        "oddUnitName": "piece",
        "openOfferPriceRule": true,
        "propGroups": [],
        "src": "approved",
    }
```

To understand tax implications, I calculated sales tax rates for 1 Market Street, San Francisco, CA 94105. I converted Chinese Yuan (CNY) to US Dollars (USD) using a currency exchange tool. I processed an image using a background removal service. Additionally, I browsed ASOS categories for the US market, explored Alibaba's top-level product categories (parent_id: 0), and searched for ergonomic office chair filters on IKEA's US website.

query: I need information about multiple e-commerce products and services across different platforms. First, check pricing and product details for an Amazon item (ASIN: B07GR5MSKD) on the German marketplace. Then, get warranty services and financing options for a Wayfair product (SKU: W003078383). Also, retrieve shipping information for an AliExpress product (ID: 4000961087745) being shipped to France. Check the status of a Walmart order (ID: 12345ABC) for a customer (email: test@example.com). Additionally, obtain a list of Ikea product categories available in the US in English, and list Asos categories for US customers. I also need currency exchange rates from USD to CHF, and sales tax information for an address in Menlo Park, CA (1 Hacker Way, 94025). Finally, show me all countries where Asos sells products.
